        <div1><pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_nhg.00048.jpg" type="recto"/>        
        <head type="main-authorial"><handShift new="#h1"/>"Church" Article.</head>
        <p>
            
            The Dutch Reformed Church
            was ecclesiasticaly dependent
            upon the Presbytery of
            Amsterdam, Holland, and
            kept up <del rend="overstrike">its</del> connection
            with its home superiors
            there, down to the time of
            the American Revolution</p></div1>
        <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_nhg.00049.jpg" type="verso"/>
        <!--<ab><handShift new="#h2"/>PLEASE PRESERVE THIS BILL.]
